last_episode_to_air.name: The Reunion
last_episode_to_air.overview: After a historic finale, the group reunites with Nick and Vanessa for a heartfelt and heated sit-down about their experience and where they're at now.

name: The Ultimatum: Marry or Move On
original_name: The Ultimatum: Marry or Move On
overview: Get hitched or call it quits? Couples put their love to the test — while shacking up with other potential matches — in a provocative reality series.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Put a ring on it — or split? Five new couples test their commitment by pairing up with different partners in another season of this social experiment.

tagline: It's time to marry or move on.

episodes.name: The Split
episodes.overview: Emotions are high--and sparks fly--as the couples part then embark on the ultimate love challenge. Can they pick a new partner, with real potential?

episodes.name: The Choice
episodes.overview: Will attraction evolve into deeper connection? Selecting a live-in match makes for flirty fun--and hurt feelings. Time for a life-changing choice.

episodes.name: New Bed, New Partner
episodes.overview: One shock follows another as an honest, tearful outburst leaves everyone speechless. Later, the accelerated trial unions kick off with pillow talk.

episodes.name: Girls & Guys Night Out
episodes.overview: Love may be blossoming, but jealousy gets in the way. We're moving fast, so meet the racer dad. The truth stings as everyone trades notes over drinks.

episodes.name: Pushing Boundaries
episodes.overview: After an evening of strained cocktail hours, couples cuddle--and implode. A forbidden meeting ends with drama as short-term spouses push each other.

episodes.name: The Changeover
episodes.overview: Major feelings emerge at the changeover. Everyone's back with their original partners, but the transition might be bumpier than anyone ever imagined.

episodes.name: Back to Reality
episodes.overview: Tears tarnish a bachelorette bash. Longtime loves try to listen and hold on to hope. The couples board the party bus to bond, awkwardly, at a winery.

episodes.name: Time to Answer the Ultimatum
episodes.overview: An all-nighter deals a blow to a fragile relationship. Can bruised feelings be soothed by a temp partner? Family weigh in with love on the line.

episodes.name: Ultimatum Day
episodes.overview: Ultimatum Day arrives. Now the couples must decide whether they'll marry the love they know, reconnect with an attractive alternative — or walk away.

episodes.name: The Reunion
episodes.overview: Where are they now? Catch up with the couples as they revisit the experience and talk about their lives since the series with Vanessa and Nick.

episodes.name: The Split
episodes.overview: The couples spend tense and tearful last nights together. Then, jealousy brews as they begin mingling amongst each other to make connections.

episodes.name: Unexpected Revelations
episodes.overview: For some, the sight of their ex dating others proves too much to bear. After a dramatic confrontation, everyone prepares to choose their live-in partner.

episodes.name: The Choice
episodes.overview: A stunning revelation shifts the group dynamics. Following the choice ceremony, the new couples move in together — there's no going back now.

episodes.name: Catching Feelings
episodes.overview: From picnics and meeting parents to heart-to-heart conversations, the trial marriages continue. Which bonds will flourish, and which will fizzle?

episodes.name: Are You The One?
episodes.overview: Time to sip and tell: brutal honesty abounds over drinks at ladies and guys night, and as harsh opinions come to light, friction grows.

episodes.name: The Changeover
episodes.overview: The fallout from cocktail hour changes several couples' perspectives. Strong words and hard truths are shared during an intense changeover.

episodes.name: Change of Heart
episodes.overview: Finally reunited, the original couples start a new round of marriages with fresh eyes. But the transition is bumpy — and even bitter — for some.

episodes.name: Time to Answer the Ultimatum
episodes.overview: With only three days of the experiment left, the couples consult with friends and family. Can romantic gestures and deep talks ease lingering doubts?

episodes.name: The Reunion
episodes.overview: After a historic finale, the group reunites with Nick and Vanessa for a heartfelt and heated sit-down about their experience and where they're at now.
